✅ 8) Utilities \& Helpers (High scoring)

⭐ What are utilities?
Answer:
Utilities are ready-made small classes used to quickly style elements without writing custom CSS.

⭐ Spacing utilities (most used)
m-3 → margin all sides
p-2 → padding all sides
mt-4 → margin-top
mb-3 → margin-bottom
ms-3 → margin-left (start)
me-3 → margin-right (end)

Text: text-center, text-danger
Display: d-flex, d-none
Background: bg-dark, bg-warning
Borders: border, rounded

