✅ 9) Responsive Design with Bootstrap

Q21 (🔥 MMI). How do you make a website responsive using Bootstrap?

Answer:
Bootstrap responsiveness is achieved by:

✅ Using grid system with breakpoints
✅ Using responsive utilities like d-none d-md-block
✅ Using responsive images: .img-fluid
✅ Using container properly

Example:

<img src="img.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Responsive">
